00:12:31.000 --> 00:12:32.999
Nothing else...

00:12:33.000 --> 00:12:33.999
Yes, just that.

00:12:34.000 --> 00:12:35.999
Could you make it more specific?

00:12:36.000 --> 00:12:38.999
Just take me exactly as I am.

00:12:39.000 --> 00:12:39.999
Simply...

00:12:40.000 --> 00:12:41.999
keep the era vague.

00:12:42.000 --> 00:12:42.999
Yes.

00:12:43.000 --> 00:12:44.999
You know—‘the prince of somewhere.’

00:12:45.000 --> 00:12:47.999
It could be inside a novel...

00:12:48.000 --> 00:12:51.999
or from some historical period.

00:12:52.000 --> 00:12:52.999
Any era.

00:12:53.000 --> 00:12:54.999
It could be in a film...

00:12:55.000 --> 00:12:55.999
or a fantasy. Honestly...

00:12:56.000 --> 00:12:57.999
I think all of them suit me.

00:12:58.000 --> 00:13:00.999
An open ending—decide for yourselves.

00:13:01.000 --> 00:13:04.999
That's the idea. Honestly, I'm just...

00:13:05.000 --> 00:13:06.999
I like that. But tell me...

00:13:07.000 --> 00:13:08.999
Are you a princess or a prince? [Laughs]

00:13:09.000 --> 00:13:09.999
I'm a prince.

00:13:10.000 --> 00:13:11.999
Yes, well...

00:13:12.000 --> 00:13:13.999
The fans call me a princess...

00:13:14.000 --> 00:13:14.999
so I simply accepted it.

00:13:15.000 --> 00:13:15.999
Okay.

00:13:16.000 --> 00:13:16.999
Actually...

00:13:17.000 --> 00:13:18.999
I can be either one. I can do it all.

00:13:19.000 --> 00:13:20.999
Exactly. You can do it all.

00:13:21.000 --> 00:13:22.999
Excellent.

00:13:23.000 --> 00:13:23.999
And on that subject...

00:13:24.000 --> 00:13:24.999
Yes.

00:13:25.000 --> 00:13:27.999
Before the stream...

00:13:28.000 --> 00:13:28.999
Mm.

00:13:29.000 --> 00:13:30.999
I realized I've gained
a clear understanding of myself.

00:13:31.000 --> 00:13:31.999
It's very clear now.

00:13:32.000 --> 00:13:34.999
Really? Once I accepted that I'm cute...

00:13:35.000 --> 00:13:37.999
I started feeling much more at ease.

00:13:38.000 --> 00:13:39.999
[Laughs]

00:13:40.000 --> 00:13:42.999
Wow. That's incredible, hyung.

00:13:43.000 --> 00:13:46.999
How much more at ease are you?

00:13:47.000 --> 00:13:48.999
At first, I couldn't really understand it.

00:13:49.000 --> 00:13:50.999
No, what I mean is...

00:13:51.000 --> 00:13:51.999
I never thought I was cute...

00:13:52.000 --> 00:13:52.999
in my entire life.

00:13:53.000 --> 00:13:54.999
But then...

00:13:55.000 --> 00:13:57.999
not long ago...

00:13:58.000 --> 00:13:59.999
during a Weverse Live, our fans...

00:14:00.000 --> 00:14:02.999
kept saying, ‘Noah is so cute.’

00:14:03.000 --> 00:14:05.999
They said it so many times.

00:14:06.000 --> 00:14:07.999
Had you really never been called cute...

00:14:08.000 --> 00:14:08.999
before in your life?

00:14:09.000 --> 00:14:09.999
Almost never.

00:14:10.000 --> 00:14:11.999
Maybe a few times, but honestly...

00:14:12.000 --> 00:14:14.999
I always thought I was far from cute.

00:14:15.000 --> 00:14:16.999
I'm not someone who normally...

00:14:17.000 --> 00:14:18.999
acts all tiny and adorable.

00:14:19.000 --> 00:14:19.999
That's what I thought.

00:14:20.000 --> 00:14:21.999
So I never really tried, but PLLI...

00:14:22.000 --> 00:14:23.999
kept saying it over and over.

00:14:24.000 --> 00:14:24.999
Eventually I acknowledged it on stream.

00:14:25.000 --> 00:14:25.999
I admitted it.

00:14:26.000 --> 00:14:26.999
What did you say?

00:14:27.000 --> 00:14:28.999
‘Okay, I admit I'm cute.’

00:14:29.000 --> 00:14:30.999
I gave them that.

00:14:31.000 --> 00:14:31.999
Once I did, I felt so much better.

00:14:32.000 --> 00:14:32.999
Ah.

00:14:33.000 --> 00:14:33.999
Ah... [Sighs]

00:14:34.000 --> 00:14:34.999
From then on, I finally...

00:14:35.000 --> 00:14:36.999
understood myself.

00:14:37.000 --> 00:14:38.999
Han Noah finally knew his place:

00:14:39.000 --> 00:14:39.999
‘I'm a cute person.’

00:14:40.000 --> 00:14:40.999
Mm.

00:14:41.000 --> 00:14:41.999
That's what I realized.

00:14:42.000 --> 00:14:43.999
I see. Then I thought about it...

00:14:44.000 --> 00:14:46.999
and PLLI also calls me sexy.

00:14:47.000 --> 00:14:47.999
What exactly are you, hyung?

00:14:48.000 --> 00:14:49.999
I don't know. Apparently I'm sexy...

00:14:50.000 --> 00:14:54.999
a prince...

00:14:55.000 --> 00:14:55.999
a princess, mature, and cute.

00:14:56.000 --> 00:14:56.999
The protagonist too.

00:14:57.000 --> 00:14:58.999
Yes. They attach every label to me.

00:14:59.000 --> 00:14:59.999
How can they give you everything?

00:15:00.000 --> 00:15:01.999
What am I supposed to do?

00:15:02.000 --> 00:15:03.999
I kept wondering what to do.

00:15:04.000 --> 00:15:04.999
I thought about it constantly.

00:15:05.000 --> 00:15:06.999
But you admitted you're cute, hyung.

00:15:07.000 --> 00:15:07.999
Now you have to show us some aegyo.

00:15:08.000 --> 00:15:08.999
Being cute and doing aegyo are different.

00:15:09.000 --> 00:15:12.999
There's natural, unintentional cuteness...

00:15:13.000 --> 00:15:14.999
and then there's deliberately acting cute.

00:15:15.000 --> 00:15:15.999
They're not the same.

00:15:16.000 --> 00:15:17.999
Then don't force it.

00:15:18.000 --> 00:15:21.999
Right. [Laughs]

00:15:22.000 --> 00:15:22.999
Yes.

00:15:23.000 --> 00:15:25.999
What? They're asking for a selfie.

00:15:26.000 --> 00:15:27.999
But hyung, you said you feel at ease now.

00:15:28.000 --> 00:15:29.999
I can't do things like that.

00:15:30.000 --> 00:15:31.999
No—hyung, just do whatever feels comfortable.

00:15:32.000 --> 00:15:32.999
Seriously, stop. I can't do it.

00:15:33.000 --> 00:15:35.999
I said stop.

00:15:36.000 --> 00:15:37.999
Since when? This is already it.

00:15:38.000 --> 00:15:39.999
What you're doing right now is cute.

00:15:40.000 --> 00:15:42.999
PLLI finds this whole thing adorable, right?

00:15:43.000 --> 00:15:43.999
Right.

00:15:44.000 --> 00:15:44.999
See? If you agree, we'll move on.

00:15:45.000 --> 00:15:47.999
Now, Bamby...

00:15:48.000 --> 00:15:48.999
I can't accept it.

00:15:49.000 --> 00:15:49.999
Bamby.

00:15:50.000 --> 00:15:51.999
What? I feel deeply uncomfortable.

00:15:52.000 --> 00:15:54.999
Being called cute genuinely stresses me out.

00:15:55.000 --> 00:15:56.999
I understand that. But you're good at aegyo.

00:15:57.000 --> 00:15:57.999
You really are.

00:15:58.000 --> 00:15:58.999
No.

00:15:59.000 --> 00:15:59.999
I'm not cute.

00:16:00.000 --> 00:16:00.999
That's ridiculous.

00:16:01.000 --> 00:16:04.999
I don't know how to do aegyo. [Laughs]

00:16:05.000 --> 00:16:06.999
Wait. But that little gesture just now...

00:16:07.000 --> 00:16:08.999
Stop doing that now.

00:16:09.000 --> 00:16:09.999
Then what should I do?

00:16:10.000 --> 00:16:11.999
Do it properly.

00:16:12.000 --> 00:16:14.999
Please stop that now.

00:16:15.000 --> 00:16:16.999
What even counts as real aegyo?

00:16:17.000 --> 00:16:18.999
You saw what just came out naturally.

00:16:19.000 --> 00:16:23.999
That was genuinely spontaneous.

00:16:24.000 --> 00:16:25.999
Don't try to make it funny.
Was that supposed to be real?

00:16:26.000 --> 00:16:27.999
You do that all the time.

00:16:28.000 --> 00:16:29.999
No! Hyung, that was...

00:16:30.000 --> 00:16:30.999
the first time I've ever done that.

00:16:31.000 --> 00:16:33.999
You do it all the time.

00:16:34.000 --> 00:16:35.999
‘When did you get here?’

00:16:36.000 --> 00:16:37.999
That one might actually be new.

00:16:38.000 --> 00:16:38.999
‘Why did you come?’

00:16:39.000 --> 00:16:40.999
Okay, okay, okay.

00:16:41.000 --> 00:16:43.999
Fine. I just saw it for the first time...

00:16:44.000 --> 00:16:46.999
so I'll accept that. Today was not easy.

00:16:47.000 --> 00:16:48.999
And then there's Yejun.

00:16:49.000 --> 00:16:51.999
He left us the words,
‘Aegyo is repetition.’

00:16:52.000 --> 00:16:54.999
That's a legendary quote.

00:16:55.000 --> 00:16:55.999
It's like one of hyung's life lessons.

00:16:56.000 --> 00:16:57.999
Right. His aegyo is more about momentum.

00:16:58.000 --> 00:16:59.999
That's what drives it.

00:17:00.000 --> 00:17:01.999
If he keeps repeating it with momentum...

00:17:02.000 --> 00:17:02.999
you have no choice but to laugh.

00:17:03.000 --> 00:17:05.999
Eventually you lose your resistance...

00:17:06.000 --> 00:17:06.999
to all that momentum.

00:17:07.000 --> 00:17:08.999
Then you think, ‘Oh, this really is cute.’

00:17:09.000 --> 00:17:10.999
Even I ended up reacting that way.

00:17:11.000 --> 00:17:11.999
It's more funny than cute.

00:17:12.000 --> 00:17:14.999
No—well, that's true.

00:17:15.000 --> 00:17:16.999
But it is kind of cute.

00:17:17.000 --> 00:17:17.999
Right. Of course it is.

00:17:18.000 --> 00:17:19.999
Isn't simply existing already cute?

00:17:20.000 --> 00:17:21.999
He has king-level cuteness. King-cute.

00:17:22.000 --> 00:17:24.999
Yes, Yejun really is king-cute.

00:17:25.000 --> 00:17:25.999
That took an unexpected turn.

00:17:26.000 --> 00:17:27.999
You really are uncomfortable with this.

00:17:28.000 --> 00:17:28.999
Okay, enough.

00:17:29.000 --> 00:17:30.999
Anyway, given my current situation...

00:17:31.000 --> 00:17:32.999
I decided...

00:17:33.000 --> 00:17:34.999
to post a poll on Bubble.

00:17:35.000 --> 00:17:36.999
What was the result?

00:17:37.000 --> 00:17:37.999
Let's check it now.

00:17:38.000 --> 00:17:40.999
When did you post it?

00:17:41.000 --> 00:17:42.999
About an hour and a half ago.

00:17:43.000 --> 00:17:43.999
Before the stream.

00:17:44.000 --> 00:17:45.999
Yes.

00:17:46.000 --> 00:17:47.999
‘Cute’ is winning by a huge margin.

00:17:48.000 --> 00:17:50.999
But turnout is still low, everyone.

00:17:51.000 --> 00:17:52.999
Why have only 32 percent voted?

00:17:53.000 --> 00:17:54.999
Only about a third.

00:17:55.000 --> 00:17:57.999
It's been an hour.
The split is 72 to 26 percent.

00:17:58.000 --> 00:17:58.999
Yes.

00:17:59.000 --> 00:18:01.999
The current result looks decisive...

00:18:02.000 --> 00:18:03.999
but only 32 percent have voted.

00:18:04.000 --> 00:18:04.999
So we still don't know.

00:18:05.000 --> 00:18:07.999
If more people...

00:18:08.000 --> 00:18:09.999
take part...

00:18:10.000 --> 00:18:12.999
the result could still change.

00:18:13.000 --> 00:18:13.999
Please don't manipulate it.

00:18:14.000 --> 00:18:14.999
Right.

00:18:15.000 --> 00:18:16.999
See? Even now...

00:18:17.000 --> 00:18:19.999
PLLI keeps calling me so cute...

00:18:20.000 --> 00:18:21.999
so I've decided to accept that I'm cute.

00:18:22.000 --> 00:18:23.999
I see. When you look at me, am I cute...

00:18:24.000 --> 00:18:25.999
or sexy?

00:18:26.000 --> 00:18:27.999
Cute. You think I'm cute?

00:18:28.000 --> 00:18:28.999
Not sexy? You're an adorable little thing.

00:18:29.000 --> 00:18:29.999
Really?

00:18:30.000 --> 00:18:30.999
Our dear Noah...

00:18:31.000 --> 00:18:32.999
Me? Yes.

00:18:33.000 --> 00:18:33.999
You're cute.

00:18:34.000 --> 00:18:34.999
Adorably so.

00:18:35.000 --> 00:18:35.999
Understood.

00:18:36.000 --> 00:18:37.999
Yes.

00:18:38.000 --> 00:18:38.999
Oh... [Snorts]

00:18:39.000 --> 00:18:39.999
Let's move on.

00:18:40.000 --> 00:18:41.999
Good.

00:18:42.000 --> 00:18:42.999
Now, there's Chobok...

00:18:43.000 --> 00:18:44.999
Chobok...

00:18:45.000 --> 00:18:46.999
Jungbok, and Malbok.

00:18:47.000 --> 00:18:48.999
Those are Boknal days.
You usually eat samgyetang then.

00:18:49.000 --> 00:18:50.999
We ate samgyetang on Chobok.

00:18:51.000 --> 00:18:51.999
Yes.

00:18:52.000 --> 00:18:52.999
I ate half a chicken.

00:18:53.000 --> 00:18:53.999
Right.

00:18:54.000 --> 00:18:54.999
I ate a whole one.

00:18:55.000 --> 00:18:55.999
Not long ago.

00:18:56.000 --> 00:18:58.999
What do you want to eat for Jungbok?

00:18:59.000 --> 00:19:00.999
Apparently it's tomorrow.

00:19:01.000 --> 00:19:02.999
Samgyetang again would be repetitive...

00:19:03.000 --> 00:19:03.999
so how about fried chicken?

00:19:04.000 --> 00:19:04.999
Fried chicken?

00:19:05.000 --> 00:19:05.999
You're eating fried chicken tomorrow?

00:19:06.000 --> 00:19:06.999
It's tomorrow?

00:19:07.000 --> 00:19:08.999
Yes.

00:19:09.000 --> 00:19:11.999
Tomorrow won't work for me.

00:19:12.000 --> 00:19:12.999
Chicken...

00:19:13.000 --> 00:19:13.999
Chicken breast.

00:19:14.000 --> 00:19:14.999
Tomorrow? Yes, chicken breast tomorrow.

00:19:15.000 --> 00:19:16.999
Right.

00:19:17.000 --> 00:19:18.999
Ah... [Sighs]

00:19:19.000 --> 00:19:21.999
But if you look at it that way...

00:19:22.000 --> 00:19:22.999
I’ve kept eating chicken breast.

00:19:23.000 --> 00:19:25.999
So every day is practically...

00:19:26.000 --> 00:19:27.999
Chobok, Jungbok, and Malbok for me.

00:19:28.000 --> 00:19:32.999
Every day repeats Jungbok.

00:19:33.000 --> 00:19:34.999
Still, chicken breast is different.

00:19:35.000 --> 00:19:39.999
Samgyetang contains...

00:19:40.000 --> 00:19:40.999
healthier ingredients.

00:19:41.000 --> 00:19:41.999
That's part of it.

00:19:42.000 --> 00:19:43.999
Do you know what samgyetang really is?

00:19:44.000 --> 00:19:45.999
Samgyetang...

00:19:46.000 --> 00:19:47.999
uses what's called a yeongye.

00:19:48.000 --> 00:19:49.999
A yeongye?

00:19:50.000 --> 00:19:50.999
Yes.

00:19:51.000 --> 00:19:51.999
It's...

00:19:52.000 --> 00:19:53.999
a young chicken. That's what yeongye means.

00:19:54.000 --> 00:19:55.999
But that young chicken...

00:19:56.000 --> 00:19:56.999
doesn't have much meat on it.

00:19:57.000 --> 00:19:58.999
Does yeong mean ‘young’?

00:19:59.000 --> 00:19:59.999
Yes.

00:20:00.000 --> 00:20:01.999
It's written with ‘young’ and the character for chicken.

00:20:02.000 --> 00:20:04.999
Right. It's a collaboration...

00:20:05.000 --> 00:20:05.999
between English and Chinese characters.

00:20:06.000 --> 00:20:06.999
Ah.

00:20:07.000 --> 00:20:07.999
A fusion. I see.

00:20:08.000 --> 00:20:09.999
Yes, and that's why it's called yeongye.

00:20:10.000 --> 00:20:12.999
But a yeongye...

00:20:13.000 --> 00:20:13.999
doesn't have much to eat.

00:20:14.000 --> 00:20:15.999
Its legs and wings are tiny.

00:20:16.000 --> 00:20:16.999
They really are.

00:20:17.000 --> 00:20:17.999
Isn't that basically a chick?

00:20:18.000 --> 00:20:18.999
Exactly. So in the end...

00:20:19.000 --> 00:20:21.999
the breast is the only substantial part.

00:20:22.000 --> 00:20:23.999
[Sighs] It's chicken breast after all.

00:20:24.000 --> 00:20:25.999
In the end...

00:20:26.000 --> 00:20:26.999
that's what it comes down to.

00:20:27.000 --> 00:20:27.999
Ah.

00:20:28.000 --> 00:20:30.999
So either way...
maybe I'll have samgyetang tomorrow.

00:20:31.000 --> 00:20:31.999
One bowl should be good.

00:20:32.000 --> 00:20:32.999
That doesn't sound bad.

00:20:33.000 --> 00:20:33.999
Samgyetang tomorrow.

00:20:34.000 --> 00:20:35.999
It has jujubes and glutinous rice inside.

00:20:36.000 --> 00:20:36.999
You know.

00:20:37.000 --> 00:20:37.999
It’s delicious, and the filling...

00:20:38.000 --> 00:20:38.999
is part of it.

00:20:39.000 --> 00:20:39.999
You enjoy all of that.

00:20:40.000 --> 00:20:42.999
That's one of its charms.

00:20:43.000 --> 00:20:44.999
This is exactly when you should eat it.

00:20:45.000 --> 00:20:46.999
Yes.

00:20:47.000 --> 00:20:48.999
Everyone, have some samgyetang tomorrow.

00:20:49.000 --> 00:20:49.999
Each of you...

00:20:50.000 --> 00:20:50.999
Yes.

00:20:51.000 --> 00:20:51.999
We can all eat it together tomorrow.

00:20:52.000 --> 00:20:52.999
Shall we? Yes, let's eat together.

00:20:53.000 --> 00:20:53.999
I'll have to get some.

00:20:54.000 --> 00:20:54.999
Right. Good.

00:20:55.000 --> 00:20:55.999
Let's all try some samgyetang.

00:20:56.000 --> 00:20:56.999
Samgyetang it is.

00:20:57.000 --> 00:20:57.999
That's decided.

00:20:58.000 --> 00:21:00.999
And this is also the first time in a while...

00:21:01.000 --> 00:21:02.999
that the two of us have done this kind of stream.

00:21:03.000 --> 00:21:04.999
It's been a long time.

00:21:05.000 --> 00:21:06.999
Do you know which stream was the last one?

00:21:07.000 --> 00:21:07.999
Dujjonku.

00:21:08.000 --> 00:21:08.999
Yes, Dujjonku.

00:21:09.000 --> 00:21:11.999
Right. This is our first since that stream.

00:21:12.000 --> 00:21:13.999
When was Dujjonku already?

00:21:14.000 --> 00:21:14.999
Dujjonku appeared and vanished in a flash.

00:21:15.000 --> 00:21:16.999
Hasn't it been a year?

00:21:17.000 --> 00:21:17.999
Something like that.

00:21:18.000 --> 00:21:19.999
Since our Dujjonku stream...

00:21:20.000 --> 00:21:21.999
Dujjonku...

00:21:22.000 --> 00:21:23.999
I think it's been about a year.

00:21:24.000 --> 00:21:24.999
It was this year.

00:21:25.000 --> 00:21:26.999
Oh, this year. Right.

00:21:27.000 --> 00:21:27.999
It was this year.

00:21:28.000 --> 00:21:30.999
Wasn't it last year? I remember...

00:21:31.000 --> 00:21:32.999
we still have it in our refrigerator.

00:21:33.000 --> 00:21:34.999
Oh, Dujjonku was popular this year.

00:21:35.000 --> 00:21:35.999
Of course.

00:21:36.000 --> 00:21:37.999
No, wait.

00:21:38.000 --> 00:21:39.999
It was January 12.

00:21:40.000 --> 00:21:41.999
Yes.

00:21:42.000 --> 00:21:43.999
So the trend began last year...

00:21:44.000 --> 00:21:45.999
and we did it in January this year.

00:21:46.000 --> 00:21:47.999
Exactly. Oh, you're right.

00:21:48.000 --> 00:21:48.999
Then it did become popular last year.

00:21:49.000 --> 00:21:50.999
But January 12 practically feels like last year.

00:21:51.000 --> 00:21:54.999
No, it doesn't. What year was it?

00:21:55.000 --> 00:21:55.999
2026?

00:21:56.000 --> 00:21:57.999
And what year is it now?

00:21:58.000 --> 00:21:59.999
2026. Then it was this year.

00:22:00.000 --> 00:22:00.999
But it feels...

00:22:01.000 --> 00:22:02.999
If only twelve days of 2026 had passed...

00:22:03.000 --> 00:22:04.999
