01:25:26.000 --> 01:25:29.999
[Noah begins the lyric]

01:25:30.000 --> 01:25:32.999
[He continues]

01:25:33.000 --> 01:25:38.999
[Noah reaches the prompt phrase]

01:25:39.000 --> 01:25:39.999
[He trails off]

01:25:40.000 --> 01:25:40.999
