01:26:10.000 --> 01:26:11.999
[Noah finishes with a sustained word]

01:26:12.000 --> 01:26:12.999
Wow.

01:26:13.000 --> 01:26:14.999
This is one possible method.

01:26:15.000 --> 01:26:17.999
