01:40:10.000 --> 01:40:12.999
[Snorts] Hyung has arched eyebrows.

01:40:13.000 --> 01:40:16.999
No, not that.

01:40:17.000 --> 01:40:20.999
Maybe around this much. No.

01:40:21.000 --> 01:40:26.999
Eyebrows are surprisingly important.

01:40:27.000 --> 01:40:27.999
[Sighs]

01:40:28.000 --> 01:40:31.999
As this progresses...

01:40:32.000 --> 01:40:32.999
he's starting to look like someone...

01:40:33.000 --> 01:40:33.999
Yes?

01:40:34.000 --> 01:40:34.999
Like...

01:40:35.000 --> 01:40:37.999
a Western general...

01:40:38.000 --> 01:40:38.999
from The Lord of the Rings.

01:40:39.000 --> 01:40:41.999
It's the hair.

01:40:42.000 --> 01:40:44.999
This may be the best one.

01:40:45.000 --> 01:40:47.999
He looks ready to wear silver armor...

01:40:48.000 --> 01:40:51.999
ride a white horse...

01:40:52.000 --> 01:40:53.999
and charge into battle.

01:40:54.000 --> 01:40:55.999
The styling is gradually coming together.

01:40:56.000 --> 01:40:56.999
We need this part.

01:40:57.000 --> 01:40:58.999
Yes.

01:40:59.000 --> 01:41:00.999
Oh, so the eyes can do that.

01:41:01.000 --> 01:41:04.999
Wow.

01:41:05.000 --> 01:41:06.999
Hyung does have a rather fierce look.

01:41:07.000 --> 01:41:08.999
Strong and intense.

01:41:09.000 --> 01:41:10.999
And over on the right...

01:41:11.000 --> 01:41:12.999
you can change their position too.

01:41:13.000 --> 01:41:14.999
Their position? Yes.

01:41:15.000 --> 01:41:15.999
Use the controls on the right.

01:41:16.000 --> 01:41:17.999
You can make them smaller or larger.

01:41:18.000 --> 01:41:18.999
Move them closer together...

01:41:19.000 --> 01:41:20.999
or farther apart.

01:41:21.000 --> 01:41:23.999
There. That's right.

01:41:24.000 --> 01:41:24.999
You can resize and move the eyes.

01:41:25.000 --> 01:41:26.999
Make them a little smaller.

01:41:27.000 --> 01:41:28.999
You can also narrow and stretch them.

01:41:29.000 --> 01:41:31.999
Stretch them upward or squeeze them.

01:41:32.000 --> 01:41:34.999
That's it.

01:41:35.000 --> 01:41:37.999
The nose needs some work.

01:41:38.000 --> 01:41:42.999
This isn't right at all.

01:41:43.000 --> 01:41:45.999
Here it is. This is the best one.

01:41:46.000 --> 01:41:47.999
I told you I'm not joking. Look.

01:41:48.000 --> 01:41:50.999
It's starting to resemble me.

01:41:51.000 --> 01:41:57.999
The lips should be pale pink.

01:41:58.000 --> 01:42:06.999
This is cute.

01:42:07.000 --> 01:42:12.999
This looks like someone from Britain.

01:42:13.000 --> 01:42:14.999
Like...

01:42:15.000 --> 01:42:17.999
A wealthy older lady. No, hyung.

01:42:18.000 --> 01:42:19.999
No, hyung. The colors aren't right yet.

01:42:20.000 --> 01:42:21.999
Someone living in Europe...

01:42:22.000 --> 01:42:24.999
Hyung is that very rich lady.

01:42:25.000 --> 01:42:26.999
That's what hyung looks like.

01:42:27.000 --> 01:42:27.999
[Laughs]

01:42:28.000 --> 01:42:29.999
Being rich sounds good. What's wrong with that?

01:42:30.000 --> 01:42:32.999
Enough. Use this one. It's perfect.

01:42:33.000 --> 01:42:34.999
One hundred percent you, hyung. [Laughs]

01:42:35.000 --> 01:42:35.999
But the lips...

01:42:36.000 --> 01:42:38.999
It's perfect. We don't need ears.

01:42:39.000 --> 01:42:40.999
The hair hides them anyway.

01:42:41.000 --> 01:42:41.999
This is fine.

01:42:42.000 --> 01:42:45.999
But here's what this resembles...

01:42:46.000 --> 01:42:47.999
the archer hyung mentioned earlier.

01:42:48.000 --> 01:42:49.999
No, it's gradually...

01:42:50.000 --> 01:42:50.999
starting to resemble someone else.

01:42:51.000 --> 01:42:53.999
It's Thor—the protagonist of Thor.

01:42:54.000 --> 01:42:56.999
Ah. Thor?

01:42:57.000 --> 01:42:57.999
The protagonist?

01:42:58.000 --> 01:43:00.999
Isn't the man who fights with an axe called Thor?

01:43:01.000 --> 01:43:02.999
Yes, that's right.

01:43:03.000 --> 01:43:05.999
It looks like Thor...

01:43:06.000 --> 01:43:07.999
after losing weight and getting plastic surgery.

01:43:08.000 --> 01:43:09.999
Ah.

01:43:10.000 --> 01:43:11.999
He came to Korea...

01:43:12.000 --> 01:43:12.999
and had surgery.

01:43:13.000 --> 01:43:13.999
Are you finished already?

01:43:14.000 --> 01:43:16.999
How do I exit? Press L and R.

01:43:17.000 --> 01:43:21.999
Exit with L and R. I pressed them.

01:43:22.000 --> 01:43:23.999
You really are bad at this.

01:43:24.000 --> 01:43:28.999
[Sighs]

01:43:29.000 --> 01:43:29.999
Wow.

01:43:30.000 --> 01:43:31.999
I won't add glasses.

01:43:32.000 --> 01:43:32.999
What is this?

01:43:33.000 --> 01:43:37.999
Ah.

01:43:38.000 --> 01:43:39.999
The pupils. Got it—wait.

01:43:40.000 --> 01:43:40.999
Look.

01:43:41.000 --> 01:43:45.999
Wow. What is that? It looks prettier.

01:43:46.000 --> 01:43:47.999
This one is hyung after recording.

01:43:48.000 --> 01:43:50.999
We can't use that.

01:43:51.000 --> 01:43:54.999
This is hyung looking worried.

01:43:55.000 --> 01:43:58.999
Let's leave that out.
I'll change the eye color.

01:43:59.000 --> 01:44:01.999
Everyone, while Bamby erases my features...

01:44:02.000 --> 01:44:05.999
and turns me into someone else...

01:44:06.000 --> 01:44:07.999
I'll perform some magic.

01:44:08.000 --> 01:44:10.999
I have a trick to show you.

01:44:11.000 --> 01:44:13.999
Out of nowhere...

01:44:14.000 --> 01:44:20.999
Yap!

01:44:21.000 --> 01:44:22.999
[Groans and shouts]

01:44:23.000 --> 01:44:27.999
Hey!

01:44:28.000 --> 01:44:30.999
PLLI...

01:44:31.000 --> 01:44:34.999
What is this? Stop it.

01:44:35.000 --> 01:44:37.999
Stop.

01:44:38.000 --> 01:44:43.999
I'm finished with the eyebrows.

01:44:44.000 --> 01:44:47.999
Thank you. Okay, got it.

01:44:48.000 --> 01:44:48.999
The eyebrows, just once more.

01:44:49.000 --> 01:44:52.999
I know.

01:44:53.000 --> 01:44:57.999
Oh!

01:44:58.000 --> 01:45:04.999
This is it.

01:45:05.000 --> 01:45:05.999
Done.

01:45:06.000 --> 01:45:09.999
Now for face paint.

01:45:10.000 --> 01:45:16.999
Face painting.

01:45:17.000 --> 01:45:21.999
There are a few options. Use this.

01:45:22.000 --> 01:45:28.999
This one isn't bad either.

01:45:29.000 --> 01:45:30.999
That isn't a mole.

01:45:31.000 --> 01:45:32.999
A pimple appeared there...

01:45:33.000 --> 01:45:35.999
then disappeared after keeping me awake.

01:45:36.000 --> 01:45:37.999
It left a permanent mark.

01:45:38.000 --> 01:45:38.999
Isn't that what happened?

01:45:39.000 --> 01:45:48.999
No.

01:45:49.000 --> 01:45:50.999
Done. How do I finish?

01:45:51.000 --> 01:45:51.999
You're finished?

01:45:52.000 --> 01:45:56.999
Yes.

01:45:57.000 --> 01:46:01.999
[Laughs]

01:46:02.000 --> 01:46:04.999
Now make the body.

01:46:05.000 --> 01:46:07.999
We need to set the height. [Laughs]

01:46:08.000 --> 01:46:09.999
Wow.

01:46:10.000 --> 01:46:13.999
About this much.

01:46:14.000 --> 01:46:17.999
What is this? Should we add muscles, hyung?

01:46:18.000 --> 01:46:19.999
No. Hyung is slim.

01:46:20.000 --> 01:46:21.999
Keep him slender.

01:46:22.000 --> 01:46:23.999
About...

01:46:24.000 --> 01:46:24.999
this much.

01:46:25.000 --> 01:46:27.999
Done. What now?

01:46:28.000 --> 01:46:30.999
Name: Noah.

01:46:31.000 --> 01:46:31.999
[Laughs]

01:46:32.000 --> 01:46:37.999
No-ah.

01:46:38.000 --> 01:46:40.999
That isn't N. Use B.

01:46:41.000 --> 01:46:41.999
Wow.

01:46:42.000 --> 01:46:45.999
Confirm.

01:46:46.000 --> 01:46:49.999
We should add a symbol.

01:46:50.000 --> 01:46:51.999
Hmm.

01:46:52.000 --> 01:46:54.999
Try putting a flower beside the name.

01:46:55.000 --> 01:46:56.999
Like this.

01:46:57.000 --> 01:46:58.999
My name is Noah.

01:46:59.000 --> 01:47:00.999
Yes.

01:47:01.000 --> 01:47:01.999
My name is King. Hyung...

01:47:02.000 --> 01:47:03.999
do you want princess or prince?

01:47:04.000 --> 01:47:05.999
Choose prince.

01:47:06.000 --> 01:47:09.999
Is there an alien option? No.

01:47:10.000 --> 01:47:12.999
Ah.

01:47:13.000 --> 01:47:13.999
[Gasps] You're putting me through a test.

01:47:14.000 --> 01:47:17.999
[Snorts]

01:47:18.000 --> 01:47:18.999
Stay still. You didn't know my birthday.

01:47:19.000 --> 01:47:20.999
Remember?

01:47:21.000 --> 01:47:29.999
You learned it and forgot immediately.

01:47:30.000 --> 01:47:32.999
I didn't forget. Wow.

01:47:33.000 --> 01:47:36.999
Isn't that my age?

01:47:37.000 --> 01:47:40.999
What? Why are there so many options?

01:47:41.000 --> 01:47:45.999
This humble one's name is Noah.

01:47:46.000 --> 01:47:49.999
Yes.

01:47:50.000 --> 01:47:53.999
All right.

01:47:54.000 --> 01:47:55.999
Actually, knowing the 23rd...

01:47:56.000 --> 01:47:56.999
might be better than nothing.

01:47:57.000 --> 01:47:58.999
At least you knew February.

01:47:59.000 --> 01:48:00.999
I'm grateful for that.

01:48:01.000 --> 01:48:02.999
I'm not joking. I truly am.

01:48:03.000 --> 01:48:03.999
No jokes.

01:48:04.000 --> 01:48:05.999
Seriously.

01:48:06.000 --> 01:48:06.999
I'm not joking.

01:48:07.000 --> 01:48:08.999
Someone told you the answer.

01:48:09.000 --> 01:48:10.999
Who told me? Nobody said anything.

01:48:11.000 --> 01:48:11.999
Not just now.

01:48:12.000 --> 01:48:12.999
The person beside you.

01:48:13.000 --> 01:48:15.999
This humble one's name is... [Laughs]

01:48:16.000 --> 01:48:16.999
I look forward to your kindness.

01:48:17.000 --> 01:48:19.999
This humble one's name is Noah.

01:48:20.000 --> 01:48:28.999
Please take good care of me.

01:48:29.000 --> 01:48:30.999
Who is that supposed to be?

01:48:31.000 --> 01:48:36.999
Okay.

01:48:37.000 --> 01:48:40.999
Is this some kind of MBTI test?

01:48:41.000 --> 01:48:43.999
This isn't easy.

01:48:44.000 --> 01:48:44.999
That ending is very blunt.

01:48:45.000 --> 01:48:46.999
PLLI might misunderstand.

01:48:47.000 --> 01:48:52.999
Really? Please don't misunderstand.

01:48:53.000 --> 01:48:54.999
Seriously, don't misunderstand.

01:48:55.000 --> 01:48:56.999
[Panting]

01:48:57.000 --> 01:48:59.999
What does that mean?

01:49:00.000 --> 01:49:02.999
Right, right.

01:49:03.000 --> 01:49:04.999
Wow, it simply dismisses people.

01:49:05.000 --> 01:49:06.999
This result...

01:49:07.000 --> 01:49:09.999
says ‘proactive, relentless effort type.’

01:49:10.000 --> 01:49:11.999
The higher the goal, the more motivated you become...

01:49:12.000 --> 01:49:16.999
but you're also a little careless.

01:49:17.000 --> 01:49:22.999
You turned him into a fish skeleton.

01:49:23.000 --> 01:49:25.999
Are we finished?

01:49:26.000 --> 01:49:27.999
We need to play with him.

01:49:28.000 --> 01:49:29.999
This is the right door, isn't it?

01:49:30.000 --> 01:49:33.999
Here we go.

01:49:34.000 --> 01:49:48.999
[Game sounds]

01:49:49.000 --> 01:49:54.999
[Laughs]

01:49:55.000 --> 01:49:56.999
[Laughs]

01:49:57.000 --> 01:49:58.999
Why are you tormenting him?
Where should I touch?

01:49:59.000 --> 01:50:04.999
Somewhere else. His stomach?

01:50:05.000 --> 01:50:12.999
Oh, I'm supposed to pet him?

01:50:13.000 --> 01:50:16.999
Now leave the house.

01:50:17.000 --> 01:50:21.999
[Snorts]

01:50:22.000 --> 01:50:23.999
Hmm.

01:50:24.000 --> 01:50:28.999
So this is how the controls work. Okay.

01:50:29.000 --> 01:50:31.999
You control him with this.

01:50:32.000 --> 01:50:34.999
Okay, okay.

01:50:35.000 --> 01:50:37.999
Put everything down. Is Yejun okay?

01:50:38.000 --> 01:50:39.999
Are you all right?

01:50:40.000 --> 01:50:43.999
Yes.

01:50:44.000 --> 01:50:45.999
Why are Yejun's double eyelids so thick?

01:50:46.000 --> 01:50:46.999
That looks rather greasy.

01:50:47.000 --> 01:50:50.999
Far too greasy.

01:50:51.000 --> 01:50:54.999
Half his eye is double eyelid.

01:50:55.000 --> 01:50:58.999
I think I did a better job.

01:50:59.000 --> 01:51:00.999
Who made Yejun-hyung? Hamin.

01:51:01.000 --> 01:51:05.999
Hmm.

01:51:06.000 --> 01:51:06.999
Still...

01:51:07.000 --> 01:51:07.999
it is him.

01:51:08.000 --> 01:51:09.999
It isn't great, but...

01:51:10.000 --> 01:51:11.999
the longer you look, the more it feels right.

01:51:12.000 --> 01:51:12.999
Exactly.

01:51:13.000 --> 01:51:15.999
That's what I was aiming for.

01:51:16.000 --> 01:51:26.999
It gradually draws you in.

01:51:27.000 --> 01:51:29.999
Is this Hamin?

01:51:30.000 --> 01:51:30.999
Hmm.

01:51:31.000 --> 01:51:31.999
Press X.

01:51:32.000 --> 01:51:36.999
Hello, Your Excellency.

01:51:37.000 --> 01:51:38.999
We need to see his expressions too.

01:51:39.000 --> 01:51:43.999
Ah.

01:51:44.000 --> 01:51:45.999
Oh, that's not it.

01:51:46.000 --> 01:51:48.999
Hey, hey, hey.

01:51:49.000 --> 01:52:01.999
Oh, like this.

01:52:02.000 --> 01:52:04.999
Oh, a level-up.

01:52:05.000 --> 01:52:18.999
Huh? It's giving us a gift: a mini personality.

01:52:19.000 --> 01:52:21.999
How do I greet them with applause?

01:52:22.000 --> 01:52:24.999
You feel a little different now.

01:52:25.000 --> 01:52:27.999
That's how it feels.

01:52:28.000 --> 01:52:34.999
What is this?

01:52:35.000 --> 01:52:36.999
Would you like to do it for me?

01:52:37.000 --> 01:52:38.999
Hmm.

01:52:39.000 --> 01:52:43.999
Oh, someone important.

01:52:44.000 --> 01:52:45.999
A little neater.

01:52:46.000 --> 01:52:50.999
Oh, a present.

01:52:51.000 --> 01:52:52.999
Clothes.

01:52:53.000 --> 01:52:55.999
For Hamin's everyday clothes...

01:52:56.000 --> 01:52:58.999
Let's dress him in something he likes.

01:52:59.000 --> 01:53:01.999
Hamin likes this kind of look... Ah, this is a bit...

01:53:02.000 --> 01:53:06.999
This one is a little...

01:53:07.000 --> 01:53:08.999
You know the kind of look Hamin likes.

01:53:09.000 --> 01:53:09.999
Over there.

01:53:10.000 --> 01:53:11.999
But that leans too heavily into his own style.

01:53:12.000 --> 01:53:12.999
That's why.

01:53:13.000 --> 01:53:14.999
Yes.

01:53:15.000 --> 01:53:15.999
Hamin likes the one on the right.

01:53:16.000 --> 01:53:17.999
He likes tops like that, you know.

01:53:18.000 --> 01:53:19.999
Oh, really?

01:53:20.000 --> 01:53:21.999
Wow, I really can't picture that.

01:53:22.000 --> 01:53:23.999
Right. Or the one underneath.

01:53:24.000 --> 01:53:24.999
He likes this one too.

01:53:25.000 --> 01:53:29.999
This is completely Bamby's style, though.

01:53:30.000 --> 01:53:32.999
There. Yeah.

01:53:33.000 --> 01:53:35.999
A mini style.

01:53:36.000 --> 01:53:40.999
We're styling him, right?

01:53:41.000 --> 01:53:46.999
Oh, it's on the left. Okay, okay.

01:53:47.000 --> 01:53:50.999
Done.

01:53:51.000 --> 01:53:54.999
Done. That's it.

01:53:55.000 --> 01:53:55.999
Right.

01:53:56.000 --> 01:53:58.999
Oh, that suits him.

01:53:59.000 --> 01:53:59.999
Okay.

01:54:00.000 --> 01:54:02.999
What do we do now?

01:54:03.000 --> 01:54:03.999
Done.

01:54:04.000 --> 01:54:06.999
Good job, our Hamin.

01:54:07.000 --> 01:54:09.999
Okay, okay.

01:54:10.000 --> 01:54:11.999
Okay, okay, okay. I'll open it

01:54:12.000 --> 01:54:13.999
for you.

01:54:14.000 --> 01:54:15.999
All right.

01:54:16.000 --> 01:54:18.999
This game is really hard. You're

01:54:19.000 --> 01:54:21.999
really bad at it. Why are you so bad

01:54:22.000 --> 01:54:28.999
at the controls?

01:54:29.000 --> 01:54:29.999
Let's go outside.

01:54:30.000 --> 01:54:30.999
Why are you so bad at this?

01:54:31.000 --> 01:54:32.999
Oh, I do this, right?

01:54:33.000 --> 01:54:37.999
Yeah, that's right.

01:54:38.000 --> 01:54:39.999
I'm asking why you're so bad at it.

01:54:40.000 --> 01:54:46.999
What are you doing?

01:54:47.000 --> 01:54:47.999
I need to listen to this too. Okay.

01:54:48.000 --> 01:54:51.999
Okay, got it. Got it.

01:54:52.000 --> 01:54:53.999
Oh, I have to play before I can make

01:54:54.000 --> 01:55:00.999
the next person. I didn't know.

01:55:01.000 --> 01:55:03.999
Apparently you have to play before you earn

01:55:04.000 --> 01:55:05.999
the right to make the next one, everyone.

01:55:06.000 --> 01:55:08.999
We have to progress.

01:55:09.000 --> 01:55:09.999
You want the mood changed? Okay.

01:55:10.000 --> 01:55:10.999
Just wait.

01:55:11.000 --> 01:55:11.999
Yes. Progressing isn't easy either.

01:55:12.000 --> 01:55:13.999
It really isn't, because...

01:55:14.000 --> 01:55:14.999
there are so many things we want,

01:55:15.000 --> 01:55:16.999
and as you can see, even the graphics

01:55:17.000 --> 01:55:18.999
make this a very complicated game.

01:55:19.000 --> 01:55:21.999
There, it opened. Once this is done,

01:55:22.000 --> 01:55:23.999
we can make one. Now, our Hamin...

01:55:24.000 --> 01:55:24.999
Our Hamin.

01:55:25.000 --> 01:55:26.999
He's progressing things even here.

01:55:27.000 --> 01:55:29.999
The MC is dragging this forward here too.

01:55:30.000 --> 01:55:31.999
It can't be helped.

01:55:32.000 --> 01:55:34.999
From the Studio Playform Center, news

01:55:35.000 --> 01:55:38.999
about the residents...

01:55:39.000 --> 01:55:41.999
[Snorts]

01:55:42.000 --> 01:55:44.999
We've finished Eunho too. His style

01:55:45.000 --> 01:55:46.999
looks great.

01:55:47.000 --> 01:55:50.999
Eunho likes interior design and things like that.

01:55:51.000 --> 01:55:53.999
Right? We need to choose the cheapest option

01:55:54.000 --> 01:55:54.999
for the best value.

01:55:55.000 --> 01:55:56.999
Yes.

01:55:57.000 --> 01:55:57.999
Thank you.

01:55:58.000 --> 01:55:59.999
Great.

01:56:00.000 --> 01:56:02.999
No. For things like this, Eunho...

01:56:03.000 --> 01:56:03.999
Please help me again next time.

01:56:04.000 --> 01:56:08.999
Sure.

01:56:09.000 --> 01:56:10.999
Press A.

01:56:11.000 --> 01:56:11.999
Welcome.

01:56:12.000 --> 01:56:12.999
You're seriously terrible at this.

